name: BMO SIA Focused Canadian Equity Fund
longDescription: This funds objective is to provide longterm capital growth by investing primarily in a portfolio of Canadian equities. The fundamental investment objectives may only be changed with the approval of a majority of the votes cast at a meeting of unitholders called for that purpose. The fund invests primarily in a portfolio of Canadian equities.
